Shout by Siggi
BlockedParentJan 31, 2026 1:46 AM

While this is an another classic Buddy-Action movie, I really liked it anyway ;-) This is certainly due to the fact that I like Mamoa and Bautista and that they deliver excellent performances.
I also like Morrison and Baccarin, so they round up my positive appreciation.
The action is also good and they refrain from overloading the movie with action, which is positive and allows the characters to shine.
Excellent popcorn entertainment.
